project.name: abstractSyntax_mm
project.description: Abstract syntax metamodel of the Governance DSL

33cf9c00-378a-4615-8ea5-195787974756.constraint:
context VotingPolicy inv ratioValue:
  self.ratio >= 0.0 and self.ratio <= 1.0

55b0c2c5-a149-4484-aa21-166259cb7969.constraint:
context Participant inv voteValue:
  self.vote_value >= 0.0 and self.vote_value <= 2.0

91a2d1ea-ed66-470c-98cc-58277729fd6c.constraint:
context Agent inv agentAttributes:
  self.confidence >= 0.0 and self.confidence <= 1.0 and
  self.autonomy_level >= 0.0 and self.autonomy_level <= 1.0 and
  self.explainability >= 0.0 and self.explainability <= 1.0
